Package com.github.moribund.net.packets.account

All packets that are related to accounts (account creation, logging out, etc.) are located in this package.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DrawNewPlayerPacket
    An instruction by the server to the client to draw a new Player onto the screen.
    LoginPacket
    The response from the server that a Player has logged in.
    LoginRequestPacket
    The request sent by the client to the server that a person is making an account, so it must register that request and follow instructions to handle the player server-sided.
    LogoutPacket
    A packet that indicates a player has disconnected.

Package com.github.moribund.net.packets.account Description

All packets that are related to accounts (account creation, logging out, etc.) are located in this package.
